Class FlashOverlayCreative

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FlashOverlayCreative
extends BaseFlashCreative
implements java.io.Serializable
    An overlay Creative that displays a Flash-based ad and is served via VAST 2.0 XML. Overlays cover part of the video content they are displayed on top of. This creative is read-only.
